      "date": "2013-01-30 22:51:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI just realized that these HSM RPCs are not rate- or otherwise limited in any way so a bad person might start thousands of them from a single client, which is bad.\nWe probably should plug them into max_inflight somehow, Andreas is filing a bug for this.",
